user_question: How can I incorporate a steampunk theme into my living room decor?
final_answer: To incorporate a steampunk theme into your living room decor, use a color palette of browns, coppers, and brass. Include vintage furniture, industrial lighting, and accessories like gears, clocks, and maps. Consider adding a feature wall with exposed brick or wood paneling.
